==English==
===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[proximus]]'' "nearness, proximity" and ''[[centauri]]'' "of the [[constellation]] [[Centaurus]]".

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Proxima Centauri'''
#{{star}}: A [[red dwarf]] [[star]], part of the [[Alpha Centauri]] [[system]]. It is the nearest star to [[Earth]]'s [[solar system]].

